Ingredients for Cinnamon Filling:

1/2 cup packed brown sugar

3tsp cinnamon

1/8 tsp salt

1/4 cup white granulated sugar

Ingredients for Icing:

1 cup powdered sugar 2 tbs butter, softened

1 tsp vanilla

1 tbs milk (orange juice works as well)




Ingredients for Rolls:

2 1/2 cups all purpose flour (Plus you will need some extra for when you roll out dough) 3 tbs white granulated sugar

1 1/4 cup buttermilk (if you don't have buttermilk make your

own, recipe here)

6 tbs melted butter

1 1/4 teaspoons baking powder 1/2 teaspoon baking soda 1/2 teaspoon salt
